long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Plugin will change Progress Bars and Scrubber for all Youtube videos.

Play and Load Progress Bars will be changed to rainbow and animated night sky.
Default Youtube scrubber will be chaged to Animated Nyan Cat.
